Name: Rating Star
AttributesDescription: After completing a simulation in Tidal Defense Simulator, you receive Rating Stars based on your performance. They can be used to unlock Overwatch Protocols.
BgDescription: The Rating Star measures a participant's overall ability in handling threats. Only those who demonstrate exceptional leadership and tactical skills during the simulation are granted higher, more advanced access permissions.
